 \"the occasion\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"their friends\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"families\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"a great way\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire team\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chief Executive of the Olympic Federation of Ireland, Peter Sherrard, echoed her words, saying it was an opportunity to have everyone together with their families, which had not been possible after the Toyko Olympics because of Covid-19.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.41125780485559144, \"rank\": 0.7062096176070275, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherrard_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9957567039151362, \"rank\": 0.004261378374783714, \"text\": \"Sherrard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherrard_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherrard_High_School\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Chief Executive\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Federation\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"her words\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"their families\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the Toyko Olympics\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid-19\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes, all wearing their Team Ireland green and white tracksuit, said it was emotional to see everyone but welcomed the opportunity to reflect on their achievements.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.937835235544683e-19, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"their achievements\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sophie Becker, said she relished her time at the games but also described how it can take time to readjust after the \\\"buzz\\\" of it and going back to the calm of daily life.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\", \"score\": 0.9999944927823652, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sophie Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"buzz\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the calm\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"daily life\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is, however, enjoying having the time to meet friends again and \\\"doing normal stuff like grocery shopping \\\".\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [], \"nou