://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"future success\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Olympic games\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fintan McCarthy, a double Olympic gold medalist, is grateful for the platform that this Olympics and Ireland's success has given to rowing and he is looking forward to continuing his achievements on the water.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintan McCarthy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999828378351, \"rank\": 1.7162119582807084e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a double Olympic gold medalist\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"his achievements\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said more investment in Irish sport was visible in Paris and he hopes this will continue.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9981827409545636, \"rank\": 0.0013731680527912917, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2671,